node.text:
This recipe is the perfect dessert for you! 

COOKIE DOUGH MOUSSE CAKE
INGREDIENTS
Cookie Dough:
¾ cups butter, softened
¾ cup brown sugar
¼ cup granulated sugar
1 ½ cups flour
1 tsp salt
1 tsp vanilla
2 tsp milk
1 cup chocolate chips
Mousse:
200g dark chocolate, chopped fine
3/4 cup whipping cream, hot
2 1/4 cup whipping cream, cold
1 tsp vanila
2 tbsp icing sugar
2 cups heavy cream, hot
454g dark chocolate finely chopped

 #delicious #foodgoals #nobakedessert #chocolatecake #noleftovers

node.text:
...are we just giving you this Peanut Butter Cheesecake for the fun of it?

INGREDIENTS
125g plain flour
225g sugar
38g unsweetened cocoa powder
1 tsp baking powder
¾ tsp baking soda
½ tsp salt
½ tsp instant coffee
125ml whole milk
63 ml vegetable oil
1 large egg
1 tsp vanilla extract
125ml boiling water
1 1/2 cups heavy cream
1 1/4 cup creamy peanut butter, not natural
575g cream cheese, softened to room temperature
1 1/4 cup powdered sugar
250ml heavy cream
2 tbsp clear corn syrup
125g milk chocolate finely chopped

CHICKEN PARM MAC AND CHEESE

INGREDIENTS
2 chicken breasts
150g plain flour
1 tsp dried Italian seasoning
2 eggs, whisked
140g panko breadcrumbs 
30g grated parmesan cheese
Oil for shallow frying
 
30g butter
30g flour
500ml milk
½ tsp mustard powder
¼ tsp paprika
? ? tsp nutmeg
Salt and pepper to taste
400g cooked macaroni
100g grated mozzarella,
100g grated cheddar
50g grated gruyere
 
250g tomato pasta sauce 
50g grated mozzarella cheese
Fresh basil leaves

node.text:
CHICKEN PARM SPAGHETTI PIE

INGREDIENTS
* 	2 chicken breasts, butterflied
* 	Salt & pepper, to season
* 	100g flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten
* 	180g panko breadcrumbs
* 	1 ltr vegetable oil, for frying
* 	800g spaghetti
* 	150g parmesan
* 	5 eggs
* 	250ml double cream
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1/2 tbsp black pepper
* 	Sliced mozzarella
* 	1 tablespoon olive oil
* 	1 large onion chopped
* 	2 teaspoons minced garlic
* 	400g tomato passata
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
* 	1 teaspoon dried Italian herbs
* 	1 teaspoon sugar

This recipe is the perfect dessert for you! 

COOKIE DOUGH MOUSSE CAKE
INGREDIENTS
Cookie Dough:
¾ cups butter, softened
¾ cup brown sugar
¼ cup granulated sugar
1 ½ cups flour
1 tsp salt
1 tsp vanilla
2 tsp milk
1 cup chocolate chips
Mousse:
200g dark chocolate, chopped fine
3/4 cup whipping cream, hot
2 1/4 cup whipping cream, cold
1 tsp vanila
2 tbsp icing sugar
2 cups heavy cream, hot
454g dark chocolate finely chopped

node.text:
Slide into the weekend with these Teriyaki Beef Sliders

INGREDIENTS
* 	1 tbsp groundnut oil
* 	2 lb sliced rump steak
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 1/2 tbsp Chinese five spice
* 	1 tbsp oil
* 	1 tbsp sesame seeds
* 	3 garlic cloves, crushed
* 	5cm ginger, finely diced
* 	1 1/2 cups beef stock
* 	3 tbsp dark soy sauce
* 	1 tbsp sesame oil
* 	2 tbsp sugar
* 	2 tbsp corn starch
* 	1 tsp water
Slaw
* 	1/4 red cabbage, finely shredded
* 	1 large carrot, finely shredded
* 	1 apple, finely shredded
* 	4 spring onions, sliced
* 	1 red chilli, sliced
* 	1 cup mayonnaise
* 	1 lime, juiced
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 cup chopped coriander

Boursin, Nduja AND Crab Linguine by the sea?? We're ready!

#linguine  #noleftovers #foodforthought #foodoftheday #summerrecipes

4 easy creamy sausage pasta recipes - comforting, creamy and perfect for sharing!

Tuscan sausage lasagna 
INGREDIENTS
* 	2 tbsp mild olive oil
* 	1 red chilli, finely diced
* 	2 garlic cloves, finely diced
* 	1 red onion, finely chopped
* 	3 mixed peppers
* 	9 Italian sausages, squeezed from their casings
* 	150g mixed tomatoes
* 	2 tbsp plain flour
* 	100ml white wine
* 	200ml chicken stock
* 	200ml whole milk
* 	1 jar sun dried tomatoes, drained
* 	Cooked spinach, 300g
* 	1 tbsp sea salt
* 	1 tbsp pepper
* 	lasagna sheets
* 	200g grated mozzarella
* 	40g grated parmesan

Creamy tomato and sausage pasta bake 
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 onion, chopped
* 	1 garlic, chopped 
* 	100g chestnut mushrooms, finely chopped
* 	6 sausages, meat removed from skins
* 	1 jar of passata
* 	100ml white wine
* 	2 cups of chicken stock
* 	1/2 tsp chilli flakes
* 	1 tsp sugar
* 	50ml double cream
* 	100g parmesan
* 	300g conchiglie pasta shells, cooked
* 	75g grated mozzarella
* 	75g cheddar
* 	75g fresh breadcrumbs
* 	2 tbsp dried rosemary

Cajun chicken sausage pasta

INGREDIENTS
3tablespoons of extra virgin olive oil
2 chicken breasts, cut into bite-sized pieces
14 oz smoked sausage, sliced diagonally
4 cloves of garlic, minced
3 1/2 cups low-sodium chicken broth
2 cups of heavy cream
450g dry penne pasta
2 tbsp of Cajun seasoning plus more for topping
1 cup shredded parmesan cheese
1/4 cup  parsley, finely chopped

Creamy sausage parpadelle
INGREDIENTS
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	1 large brown onion, diced
* 	2 cloves garlic
* 	1 tbsp fennel seeds
* 	8 sausages, squeezed from casings
* 	150ml white wine
* 	1 tsp chilli flakes
* 	300ml chicken stock
* 	1 can chopped tomatoes
* 	2 tbsp tomato puree
* 	3 tbsp double cream
* 	1 tsp black pepper
* 	1 tsp sea salt
* 	30g parmesan, grated
* 	400g parpadelle
* 	200g mozzarella, torn
* 	Handful fresh basil, sliced
 #staplerecipes #mealprep #foodprep #chefmode #pastamaster #pantryorganization #pastarecipe #recipeshare #pantryprep #easyrecipes

node.text:
...are we just giving you this Peanut Butter Cheesecake for the fun of it?

INGREDIENTS
125g plain flour
225g sugar
38g unsweetened cocoa powder
1 tsp baking powder
¾ tsp baking soda
½ tsp salt
½ tsp instant coffee
125ml whole milk
63 ml vegetable oil
1 large egg
1 tsp vanilla extract
125ml boiling water
1 1/2 cups heavy cream
1 1/4 cup creamy peanut butter, not natural
575g cream cheese, softened to room temperature
1 1/4 cup powdered sugar
250ml heavy cream
2 tbsp clear corn syrup
125g milk chocolate finely chopped
100g dark chocolate finely chopped
Finely chopped peanuts and chocolate shavings

#twistedfood #twisteddessert #cake #yummy #satisfying #satisfyingvideo #sweet #cheesecake #dessert #peanutbutter #bakersgonnabake #cakestagram

One way to step up any recipe? Wrap it in bacon! This one is perfect for your summer BBQ’s this week!

BACON WRAPPED JALAPENO POPPER CHICKEN ROLL-UPS

INGREDIENTS
* 	3 chicken breasts
* 	300g cream cheese
* 	100g mozzarella, finely grated
* 	100g cheddar, finely grated
* 	3 tbsp pickled jalapenos, finely chopped
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 tsp grated black pepper
* 	18 slices streaky bacon
